## Development Guidelines

### Code Quality Standards (MANDATORY)
```bash
# ALWAYS run before committing
pnpm run fix-all       # Auto-fix everything  
pnpm run check-all     # Verify all passes
```

### Code Style
- **TypeScript**: Strict settings, explicit types, avoid `any`
- **React/Next.js**: App Router patterns, Server Components preferred
- **Performance**: System fonts only, minimal dependencies
- **Styling**: Tailwind utility classes, mobile-first responsive

### Content Guidelines
- **Professional yet approachable** tone
- **Emphasize infrastructure expertise** and consumer empathy
- **Position projects** as infrastructure validation, not just products
- **Focus on partnerships** and infrastructure applications

## Performance Requirements (CRITICAL)
- **System fonts only** - never add Google Fonts
- **Minimal JavaScript** - maintain ~102kB shared bundle
- **Static generation** for all pages  
- **Mobile-first responsive** design
- **Zero external font requests**

